{
  "stem": "5248.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well he worked, and-- or-- or sometimes he was just hiding because he was too young, clearly, and we were frightened about him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to take orders from Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, sometimes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to walk on a-- not on a-- on-- not on a sidewalk, but--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the streets.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I can-- I think, I don't remember a whole day, actually.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Back to the camp, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I say again, my mother always-- I think my brother sometimes did all the cooking and buying bread.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bread was the main thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to pay fortune.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well that was-- that was till-- it lasted approximately till fall, December, '43.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then not-- yes, but then it-- it became clear that it's going-- that we're not going to make-- that the camp won't last much longer.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my mother start making, again, effort that somebody takes us out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very hard to find people who will be willing to do such things because there was a death penalty for both those who were Jews and those who were hiding the Jews, so it was very dangerous for the people.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were-- some of them were shot same way as-- they are now being honored in Israel as righteous-- as righteous Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it did not happen-- but still they lost their life, or sometimes they were put in prison and treated very badly.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So people were actually frightened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did not know that many people in Lwow by then, because in meantime, we lived in Rowne.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the contacts were lost, and many Polish people left or start leaving Lwow, moving farther to Krakow, or Warsaw, which was considered to be a safer place.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
